<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.4.9">
<l>paṭṭa pōteḻu pōtaṟiyāḷvirai</l>
<l>maṭṭa lartaṇṭuḻā yeṉṉuñcuṭar</l>
<l>vaṭṭa vāynuti nēmiyīrnuma</l>
<l>tiṭṭa meṉkoliv vēḻaikkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The time [the sun] sinks, the time it rises she doe not know.</l>
<l>“O cool Tulsi with scented honey blossoms”, she says.</l>
<l>You with the glowing, round, sharp-edged discus,</l>
<l>what is you wish for this simple [girl]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
